Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.13,0:00:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.06,0:00:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要引退了呢   是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.13,0:00:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.07,0:00:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为现在是最充实的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.14,0:00:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望能在大家心中留下最佳的印象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.14,0:00:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以在这时间点引退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.15,0:01:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.09,0:01:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引退想做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.09,0:01:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没决定   不过想尝试做各种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.03,0:01:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.10,0:01:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你引退后就没办法跟男优故爱喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.04,0:01:27.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点也让我有些犹豫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.11,0:01:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怕欲求不满
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.05,0:01:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会担心这件事喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.06,0:01:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟认识的男优讲这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.13,0:01:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都说感觉很寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.06,0:01:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说想来拍这片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.13,0:01:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.14,0:01:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚才说很多男优想来拍这片嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.14,0:02:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天来的的都是我精挑 细选的男优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.15,0:02:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以今天一定能做得很舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.09,0:02:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢   请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.10,0:02:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.03,0:02:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不拍了吗   不拍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.04,0:02:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我没办法跟称做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.11,0:02:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是最后一次好难过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.11,0:02:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后能见到你好开心   我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.05,0:02:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我特地跑来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.06,0:02:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是最后了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.12,0:02:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来做点之前没尝试过的做法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.13,0:02:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是怎样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.07,0:02:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平常都是进入拍片状态才能做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.13,0:03:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要两个人独处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.07,0:03:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样是不是比较能集中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.14,0:03:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导演   我有建议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.08,0:03:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独处吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.15,0:03:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么突然   这样很奇怪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.16,0:03:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是没错啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.09,0:03:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是这么多人没辨法集中啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.10,0:03:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想独处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.04,0:03:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲奈呢     可以独处吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.04,0:03:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想做吗     想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.05,0:03:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是最后了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.06,0:03:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能两人独处吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.06,0:03:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,性爱自拍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.06,0:04:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然会不太好剪片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.13,0:04:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了    可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.07,0:04:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那大家拜托出去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.14,0:04:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了   不要偷看喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.15,0:04:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.15,0:04:24.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是最后了   我们做得火热点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.16,0:04:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍不住在这里亲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.10,0:04:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.10,0:04:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到愿望真的实现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.05,0:04:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样还挺紧张的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.05,0:04:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.12,0:04:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样感觉挺害羞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.12,0:05:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不是演角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.13,0:05:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是跟平常的玲奈小姐做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.08,0:05:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是最后了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.08,0:05:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要带演技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.15,0:05:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通地做爱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.16,0:05:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得大胆点好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.10,0:05:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有在这样的条件下能做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.11,0:05:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好紧张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.11,0:06:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是最后反而更紧张了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.13,0:06:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样拍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.07,0:06:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍特写好害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.14,0:06:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没拍到你的脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.11,0:07:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴奋了吗兴奋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.06,0:07:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表情好色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.07,0:07:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶头硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.14,0:07:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.09,0:07:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿了   真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.03,0:07:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.11,0:08:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变这么湿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.05,0:08:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴奋得湿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.13,0:08:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你这样让我也兴奋起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.07,0:08:39.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.16,0:08:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蹭到肉棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.03,0:09:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.12,0:09:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己有感觉到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.12,0:09:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从刚才就湿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.13,0:09:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看内裤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.14,0:09:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多兴奋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.07,0:09:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很兴奋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.08,0:09:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.03,0:10:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.04,0:10:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变这么淫荡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.05,0:10:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.13,0:10:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个湿透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.07,0:10:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腰自己动起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.11,0:11:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼吸变得好急促
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.12,0:11:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁股抬高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.06,0:11:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被看到了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.15,0:12:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个湿透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.13,0:12:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连这里都被舔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.14,0:13:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴奋吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.15,0:13:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.06,0:14:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后再也看不到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.14,0:14:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽情舔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.15,0:14:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.11,0:14:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样舒服吗   好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.13,0:15:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.13,0:15:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.14,0:15:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.14,0:15:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚指都湿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.08,0:15:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看你的表情     好害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.16,0:15:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸到肉棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.16,0:15:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.10,0:15:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒变这么硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.12,0:16:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸硬梆梆的肉棒感觉如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.06,0:16:10.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想舔肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.07,0:16:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把脚伸直吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.08,0:16:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得比刚才还湿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.05,0:17:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.13,0:17:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.07,0:17:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没看小穴呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.14,0:17:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让我看吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.08,0:17:39.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想看肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.15,0:17:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经湿透 了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.16,0:17:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己让别人看很害羞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.03,0:17:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.04,0:18:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害羞吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.04,0:18:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害羞
