Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:50.06,0:32:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:32.10,0:33:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好淫荡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:47.05,0:33:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:15.08,0:34:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:30.09,0:35:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高潮了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:11.06,0:36:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:44.16,0:36:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:18.06,0:37:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想插
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:55.03,0:37:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要更用力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:20.11,0:40:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:24.11,0:40:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:33.04,0:42:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全身湿透了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:38.11,0:42:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高潮了好多次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:45.06,0:42:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:05.08,0:43:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体变得好奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:39.11,0:43:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:37.09,0:45:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服到快受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:51.03,0:46:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:09.05,0:47:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:35.08,0:47:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插得好深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:40.15,0:47:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不戴套好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:02.04,0:48:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:53.16,0:48:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变更湿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:01.16,0:49:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:51.08,0:49:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摇得这么淫荡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:54.15,0:49:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为很舒服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:42.07,0:50:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躺在这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:53.14,0:50:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我插进去喔    插进来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:01.15,0:51:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把硬梆梆的肉棒插进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:12.10,0:51:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:52.06,0:52:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:18.09,0:53:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能再继续插吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:31.03,0:53:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变这么硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:42.11,0:53:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:56.13,0:53:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射在里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:01.06,0:54:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接射在里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:05.07,0:54:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:14.14,0:54:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:42.04,0:54:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射了好多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:08.06,0:55:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:25.15,0:55:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看看小穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:32.09,0:55:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都流出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:41.16,0:55:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:49.04,0:55:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:59.05,0:56:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部吸干净
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:11.06,0:56:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会苦吗    不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:21.07,0:56:24.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没力气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:31.08,0:56:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚一直抖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:47.10,0:56:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做完了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:51.10,0:56:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:55.11,0:57:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:03.11,0:57:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下很棒的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:11.12,0:57:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:15.13,0:57:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴奋吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:18.06,0:57:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴奋到高潮好多次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:21.13,0:57:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想忘都忘不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:26.07,0:57:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好开心   不过要结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:30.07,0:57:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:33.14,0:57:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉有点寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:40.08,0:57:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:44.09,0:57:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定一生都无法再见面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:51.16,0:57:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个男优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:57.03,0:58:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你最爱的中年男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:00.37,0:58:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:01.04,0:58:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还挺喜欢他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:05.04,0:58:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:09.05,0:58:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好   好久不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:13.05,0:58:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概一年没见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:17.05,0:58:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:20.12,0:58:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你不拍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:24.13,0:58:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:29.07,0:58:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说弥喜欢酒我带了红酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:33.07,0:58:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:36.14,0:58:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来干杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:39.08,0:58:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特地带来的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:45.08,0:58:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个挺贵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:48.15,0:58:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不客气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:57.09,0:59:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝这么一点喔   我喝不了红酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:06.04,0:59:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:14.04,0:59:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:17.11,0:59:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我平常都喝啤酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:20.05,0:59:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喝不了啤酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:23.12,0:59:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你喜欢喝酒对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:26.06,0:59:29.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说你各种酒都会喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:29.13,0:59:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不喝Hoppy跟威士忌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:33.13,0:59:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这倒不是重点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:37.13,0:59:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不拍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:42.07,0:59:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从之前就决定了我怎么没听说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:45.14,0:59:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最近才说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:49.15,0:59:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引退后想做什么     其实没计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:57.15,1:00:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:01.16,1:00:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听到时真的打击很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:08.10,1:00:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍片时一直射不出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:13.04,1:00:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这一年见过很多女忧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:17.04,1:00:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢的就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:20.11,1:00:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢射
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:23.05,1:00:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们很少有机会见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:26.12,1:00:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来听到这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:31.05,1:00:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打击真的很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:34.12,1:00:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:37.06,1:00:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要重新考虑一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:40.13,1:00:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:43.07,1:00:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我直接跟你经纪人谈也行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:47.07,1:00:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经下定决心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:51.07,1:00:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才拍这 部引退纪念
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:00.15,1:01:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得拍最后一片
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:04.15,1:01:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是重头考虑一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:09.09,1:01:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦     我决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:13.10,1:01:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我很高兴你的心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:17.10,1:01:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时都能回来喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:26.04,1:01:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要那么沮丧     当然会啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:36.05,1:01:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请好好努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:39.12,1:01:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:46.06,1:01:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我干脆也引退吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:54.07,1:01:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这样     请继续拍
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:01.14,1:02:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真心打算引退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:07.15,1:02:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天能不停让你高潮吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:11.15,1:02:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:49.06,1:02:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吻这么激烈
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:22.16,1:03:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请好好享受
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:44.11,1:04:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我喝你的口水
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:50.15,1:09:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好激烈
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:57.09,1:10:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:00.16,1:10:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要停吗  不要停
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:16.04,1:10:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好激烈
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:44.13,1:11:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:14.16,1:12:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:53.16,1:17:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以插了吗   可以喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:03.04,1:18:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插进来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:23.15,1:24:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:29.07,1:27:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:45.08,1:29:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能重新考虑吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:49.08,1:29:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心意我很感激
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:52.15,1:29:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我已经决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:55.09,1:29:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:58.15,1:30:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么都要引退吗    是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:25.12,1:30:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来拍纪念照吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:29.12,1:30:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要拍吗一平先生    可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:35.13,1:30:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像还不太能接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:38.06,1:30:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拍了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:45.14,1:30:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚点寄给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:48.07,1:30:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你能接受吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:51.14,1:30:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话有点缠人      不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:56.08,1:30:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麽你先离开吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:59.15,1:31:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:05.16,1:31:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流好多汗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:11.16,1:31:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:16.10,1:31:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:27.04,1:31:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请先去洗澡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:30.11,1:31:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不重新考虑一下吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:33.05,1:31:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:36.12,1:31:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你的心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:48.13,1:31:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲奈小姐接下来也是想见你的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:55.07,1:31:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的    请进
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:01.08,1:32:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜欢玲奈小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:06.15,1:32:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说祢要引    退所以我忍了三天
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:14.16,1:32:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想射在你脸上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:18.16,1:32:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脸上吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:22.17,1:32:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:27.10,1:32:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍了三天吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:31.05,1:40:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太舒服了   谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:47.07,1:40:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来也是喜欢你的男优
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:53.08,1:40:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都不希望你引退
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:01.08,1:41:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是直接做也不有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:04.15,1:41:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请祢自己决定要跟谁做爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:08.16,1:41:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:11.09,1:41:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见你要引退吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:18.03,1:41:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太可惜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:21.10,1:41:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:24.04,1:41:27.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我定会让你更舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:27.11,1:41:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请跟我做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:50.07,1:41:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我比较好对不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:54.07,1:41:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还分不出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:59.14,1:42:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是我比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:23.17,1:42:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁比较好     还没办法决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:27.04,1:42:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那再来一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:47.06,1:42:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要跟谁做
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:50.13,1:42:53.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没办法决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:54.13,1:42:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看我的
